{"tid":1546023,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"共龍航空臭雞又篤灰 一齊篤返佢違反私隱啊啊啊","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T10:00:41.000Z","uid":301599,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5e6e2f547d48b79473151c0125727ff051552f62","tid":1546023,"uid":301599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbSrnch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbSrnch.jpg&h=c570a044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qiBKrU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qiBKrU.jpg&h=62d1e3bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>LEANNE CHONG LEE HUNG (人稱鄉音LEANNE)</strong><br />\n呢件犬用飛機杯係一隻來自<span style=\"color: red;\">福建</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅臭雞，一口北姑鄉音一開聲就會認得<br />\n話說呢隻臭雞日日畀狗篤西篤到爛，依家走去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">篤灰</span></strong></span>！！！！<br />\n共龍今日咁多CREW畀人炒就係因為佢！！！！！！<br />\n條鄉音八婆勁多心計，明明係犬用飛機杯<br />\n先係扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，懶熱心咁PRINT咗和理非問卷出嚟帶係身<br />\n其實係想套人TG、IG<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最撚過分嘅係趁啲 in-flight 同事傾計，<br />\n就錄人音篤灰</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經好多同路人空姐俾佢搞到冇咗份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有！最重要係點解in-flight可以錄音？<br />\n係咪即係呢隻臭雞可以隨意錄低機上面全部人講乜？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢件臭雞存在私隱問題</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要投訴到佢冇得飛唔好放過佢！！！！！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewGWKD0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewGWKD0.png&h=924d4ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢就係PRINT咗呢份問卷出嚟帶係身！<br />\n佢有好多好心嘅同事都信咗，就俾佢呃左！攞晒佢哋啲TG、IG<br />\n又開始佢計劃嘅下一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b74f109f17609be325c84bd941c7bb4d9d843c","tid":1546023,"uid":149215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:28:16.000Z","msg":"［核彈]906全民太子站獻花，極重要！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544949</a>"},{"pid":"98a061ffaa2d8fa5fe777eb8b9f1bc77da3bb010","tid":1546023,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=87f48d4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"5c9c1cecf3689d6488ef7377a0bceee841167cfd","tid":1546023,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:29:02.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br /